quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Alla woondirii malayka en pooɗooji pittaali pooɗgol cattungol
  79,2,Alla woondirii malayka en ittatɗi pittaali e newuya
  79,3,Alla woondirii lummbatooɗi lummbagol
  79,4,Alla woondarii daɗandirooji daɗndirgol
  79,5,E Alla woondirii yiilayɗi yamiroore
  79,6,ñande dimmbii dimmbatnde
  79,7,Rewa e hendu woɗndu
  79,8,ɓerɗe ɗe ñande heen na kuli
  79,9,Ndaarɗe mum en na koyi
  79,10,Hoɓe mbi*a mbela komin ruttatooɓe no min ngonirnoo
  79,11,Mbela somin ngontii ƴi*e ndappuɗe min nduttoto
  79,12,ɓe mbi*a si min nduttiima sinnda de ɗum wona duttal pertungal
  79,13,ɗuum ko haacaango wooto
  79,14,Ndeke tan ɓe ngontii wuurɓe
  79,15,taw si arii e maaɗa Yewtere fii Muusaa
  79,16,Tuma nde joom Makko noddi mbo ka caatngol Tuwaa
  79,17,"Yahu ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  79,18,Maakan mbo mbela woodanaani ma nde laaɓata e keefaraagal
  79,19,Mi feewnu ma e joom ma kulaa Mbo
  79,20,O holli mbo aaya mawɗo on
  79,21,O fennii o woopi
  79,22,Refti o runtii hombo yaha
  79,23,O renndini o noddi
  79,24,O wi*i ko miin woni joom mon ɓurɗo toowde
  79,25,Alla nanngiri mbo lepte cakkitiiɗe e gadane
  79,26,Wonii e ɗuum teskuya wonande kulɗo Alla